comments.content:
For some of the newly released typefaces I thought would be worth noting, check my series of [(blog) posts](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/for.ma/blog) wisely named ' [Type releases worth noting](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/for.ma/blog/?s=Type+releases)'. ;)

(Current) Personal favourites:  
 [Tempera](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/www.typonine.com/t9site/typonine/Tempera.html), by Nikola Djurek;  
 [John Sans](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/www.stormtype.com/typefaces-fonts-shop/families-23-john-sans) _(and Baskerville)_, by František Štorm;  
 [Trump Gothic _(West)_](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/www.canadatype.com/showfont.php?id=71), by Georg Trump / Patrick Griffin;  
 [Malaga](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/www.emigre.com/EF.php?fid=207), by Xavier Dupré;  
 [Freight _(Micro)_](http://web.archive.org/web/20120720132444/http:/www.dardenstudio.com/typefaces/freight_micro), by Joshua Darden.

Dav
